### Component 4: Fix `client_id` Consistency

#### [MODIFY] [ingest.py](file:///d:/rouca/DVM/workPlace/handoff/graph-generator/ingest.py)
- Line 117: Change `client_id = company_name.lower()...` to `client_id = f"{tenant_id}_{raw_id}"`
- This makes the deal summary's `client_id` match the graph generator's `client_id`

#### [MODIFY] [backend/main.py](file:///d:/rouca/DVM/workPlace/handoff/backend/main.py)
- In [proxy_crm_deals](file:///d:/rouca/DVM/workPlace/handoff/backend/main.py#126-155) simulator fallback: prefix `client_id` with `"default_"` for consistency

---

