## Verification Plan

1. Create tenant "AcmeCorp" (salesforce) via Hub
2. Fire a Salesforce webhook → ingest endpoint maps, stores deal + generates graph
3. Open Voice UI → Tenant Picker shows "AcmeCorp"
4. Select AcmeCorp → Role Selector shows correct roles + deal counts from Firestore
5. Select CSM → Dashboard shows deals from Firestore (not simulator)
6. Click deal → Briefing Session → agent reads graph with correct `client_id`
